{
    "publish_date": "2013-02-05T18:18:44.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT10M39S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "CHRISTIAN VON KOENIGSEGG:\nMy name is Christian von", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "0.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Koenigsegg.", 
            "dur": "0.07", 
            "start": "1.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m 40 years old and for half\nof my life, I&#39;ve been on the", 
            "dur": "3.54", 
            "start": "1.496"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "quest to be a leader in the\nhypercar industry utilizing", 
            "dur": "3.44", 
            "start": "5.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Swedish design combined with\nvisionary technical solutions.", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "8.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Our latest car, the Agera R, is\nbuilt in the old hangars of", 
            "dur": "3.5", 
            "start": "15.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a former Swedish fighter\njet squadron.", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "18.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Their symbol, a ghost, is now\nproudly painted on the back", 
            "dur": "4.17", 
            "start": "21.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "every Koenigsegg.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "25.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE ROARING]", 
            "dur": "24.073", 
            "start": "29.463"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ROBERT SERWANSKI: My name is\nRobert Serwanski, and I&#39;m a", 
            "dur": "2.63", 
            "start": "53.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "test driver of Koenigsegg.", 
            "dur": "3.002", 
            "start": "56.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE ROARING]", 
            "dur": "12.788", 
            "start": "59.168"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My job is, basically,\ntwo parts.", 
            "dur": "3.35", 
            "start": "71.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I developed the cars and how\nthey handle performance-wise,", 
            "dur": "4.41", 
            "start": "75.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I also am a part of\nthe production line.", 
            "dur": "2.78", 
            "start": "79.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Production-wise I get an\nassembled car, in one piece", 
            "dur": "3.73", 
            "start": "88.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you could say, and then\nI finalize it.", 
            "dur": "3.08", 
            "start": "92.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Finalizing means I do the wheel\nalignment, I put in the", 
            "dur": "3.44", 
            "start": "95.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "brakes, put in the\ndifferential.", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "98.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m with the guys who tune\nthe engine properly.", 
            "dur": "3.23", 
            "start": "101.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Everything is assembled by hand,\nso there are, of course,", 
            "dur": "3.09", 
            "start": "104.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "small differences in every car\nand that&#39;s why we tune every", 
            "dur": "4.28", 
            "start": "107.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car to a specific set up.", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "112.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we do a few wheel\nalignments, so everything can", 
            "dur": "3.74", 
            "start": "114.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "settle down.", 
            "dur": "1.35", 
            "start": "118.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And once everything works\nproperly, we all also check", 
            "dur": "4.75", 
            "start": "120.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "quality of the car, of course.", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "124.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Every function and every feature\nof the car must work.", 
            "dur": "3.8", 
            "start": "127.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so nothing can rattle,\nnothing can sound in the car.", 
            "dur": "3.35", 
            "start": "131.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah, and we do a lot of driving\nand we drive the cars", 
            "dur": "3.41", 
            "start": "137.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "rather hard, because they\nneed to work once", 
            "dur": "2.05", 
            "start": "140.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they get to the customer.", 
            "dur": "1.49", 
            "start": "142.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And a lot of that work is\ndone on this runway.", 
            "dur": "3.737", 
            "start": "144.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE ROARING]", 
            "dur": "7.163", 
            "start": "147.763"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a specific car we\ndid the zero to 300", 
            "dur": "3.61", 
            "start": "154.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to zero record in.", 
            "dur": "1.445", 
            "start": "158.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was in 21.19 seconds.", 
            "dur": "3.175", 
            "start": "159.981"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That was a year ago.", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "163.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It wasn&#39;t this cold and\nnot this windy.", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "164.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so, of course, it\nwas better for the", 
            "dur": "4.71", 
            "start": "167.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "performance of the car.", 
            "dur": "1.53", 
            "start": "172.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And also, right now, in the\nvideos you saw, we only run on", 
            "dur": "5.15", 
            "start": "173.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "50% bioethanol, and in the\nrecord videos, we always drive", 
            "dur": "4.09", 
            "start": "178.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "85%, which is available\nat your normal", 
            "dur": "2.1", 
            "start": "183.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "petrol station in Sweden.", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "185.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The car was just taken\nout on a day.", 
            "dur": "2.18", 
            "start": "187.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Christian gave me a call and\nsaid, shall we do test to do", 
            "dur": "4.22", 
            "start": "189.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the record?", 
            "dur": "0.806", 
            "start": "194.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we collected some equipment,\ngot out here, and", 
            "dur": "3.094", 
            "start": "194.902"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just did it, basically.", 
            "dur": "1.31", 
            "start": "197.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This was just sort of a stage in\nthe very fine approaches of", 
            "dur": "4.23", 
            "start": "199.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "producing the car, really.", 
            "dur": "1.676", 
            "start": "203.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE ROARING]", 
            "dur": "4.764", 
            "start": "205.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They gave me a call about two\nyears ago and offered a job.", 
            "dur": "5.11", 
            "start": "209.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I came here, had a few\nhours of discussion with", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "215.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Christian, and we talked about\nwhat the job was about.", 
            "dur": "3.34", 
            "start": "218.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then, obviously, there was\na testing period, where we", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "221.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "went all the job through and\nwhat&#39;s supposed to be done,", 
            "dur": "4.09", 
            "start": "224.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and how I feel about the car.", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "228.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;m still here.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "230.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A day could be everything from\ndriving for 12 or 16 hours,", 
            "dur": "4.64", 
            "start": "234.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it could be changing an\nengine or a gearbox for", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "238.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "development purpose.", 
            "dur": "1.4", 
            "start": "241.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So well, there&#39;s not one day\nthat is the other day like,", 
            "dur": "3.48", 
            "start": "243.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and that&#39;s a good thing\nabout the job, because", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "246.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you never get bored.", 
            "dur": "1.93", 
            "start": "248.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, my tools are, basically,\nit&#39;s also depending on the", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "250.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "purpose obviously.", 
            "dur": "0.85", 
            "start": "253.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Right now, I work a lot\nwith the gearbox.", 
            "dur": "3.209", 
            "start": "254.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We have our own gearbox\nmanagement, and for that I", 
            "dur": "3.341", 
            "start": "257.235"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have the engineers, and I have\na computer, and the car.", 
            "dur": "5.39", 
            "start": "260.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And also, we need to tune the\ngearbox for driving in the", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "265.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "city, or on highway, or doing\nzero to 300 to zero.", 
            "dur": "5.25", 
            "start": "268.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So if I need to tune the gearbox\nfor driving into town,", 
            "dur": "3.6", 
            "start": "274.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I obviously drive into town.", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "277.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that&#39;s of course doing\n50k and not 200.", 
            "dur": "4.412", 
            "start": "279.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE ROARING]", 
            "dur": "3.776", 
            "start": "283.918"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So everything is through one\ncable through OBD, is simply", 
            "dur": "6.512", 
            "start": "287.694"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "accessible through one program,", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "294.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one cable, one interface.", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "296.426"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So everything, I choose what I\nwould like to see, and what I", 
            "dur": "4.19", 
            "start": "298.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would like to adjust.", 
            "dur": "1.095", 
            "start": "303.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If I would like to go to a\ncertain gear, for instance, I", 
            "dur": "3.612", 
            "start": "304.241"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have the behavior of a gear,\nthe clutch, the shift time,", 
            "dur": "4.983", 
            "start": "307.853"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the torque out, everything\nwe control.", 
            "dur": "4.23", 
            "start": "312.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And everything can be logged\nwhile we do it.", 
            "dur": "3.622", 
            "start": "317.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s also the same thing here,\neven though we have thousands", 
            "dur": "2.538", 
            "start": "320.688"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of parameters, there&#39;s no\npurpose of really seeing it", 
            "dur": "3.93", 
            "start": "323.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all at once, because it would\nlook something like this, and", 
            "dur": "2.813", 
            "start": "327.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it just looks messy.", 
            "dur": "4.027", 
            "start": "329.969"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can connect that, what I see\nin the log, to what I sense.", 
            "dur": "4.71", 
            "start": "333.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I can see that, for\ninstance, OK, this clutch", 
            "dur": "2.635", 
            "start": "338.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "closes a little bit too fast\nor we don&#39;t cut the torque", 
            "dur": "3.175", 
            "start": "341.341"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fast enough, or whatever\nI see or sense.", 
            "dur": "2.615", 
            "start": "344.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then I change it.", 
            "dur": "1.375", 
            "start": "347.131"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then I drive\nit again, try.", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "348.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it takes a really long time\nto adjust, because you have a", 
            "dur": "4.12", 
            "start": "350.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "range of 1,000 to 7,000 revs.", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "354.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have seven gears.", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "357.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it&#39;s quite many cases to\nsolve and get really good.", 
            "dur": "5.97", 
            "start": "360.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a combination between\nman and machine, really.", 
            "dur": "4.24", 
            "start": "366.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think that we hope to do,\nwell, we want to do the best", 
            "dur": "2.95", 
            "start": "370.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car in the world, basically.", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "373.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I think we&#39;re on a\ngood way to do it.", 
            "dur": "1.775", 
            "start": "375.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a very extreme car in all\nends, but you can really put", 
            "dur": "5.135", 
            "start": "381.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "your grandma in it and just\nexplain the pedal function, if", 
            "dur": "3.685", 
            "start": "386.761"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "she doesn&#39;t have a pedal car\nalready, and let her drive.", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "390.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because it is, really,\nthat easy to drive.", 
            "dur": "1.93", 
            "start": "393.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Of course, it&#39;s wide and it&#39;s\nlow, and all those parts, but", 
            "dur": "3.88", 
            "start": "394.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s really easy to drive.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "398.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And of course, when you\nstart pushing it, I", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "400.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "think you need to be--", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "402.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it will not kill you, but you\nneed to know what you&#39;re doing", 
            "dur": "4.57", 
            "start": "404.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to really be able to enjoy\nthe car fully out.", 
            "dur": "4.07", 
            "start": "409.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because that is when it really\ncomes to its soul, or whatever", 
            "dur": "5.78", 
            "start": "413.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you like to call it.", 
            "dur": "2.241", 
            "start": "418.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It come alive, correct.", 
            "dur": "1.789", 
            "start": "421.137"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can still have plenty of\nfun just driving along with", 
            "dur": "3.72", 
            "start": "422.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hitting full throttle and full\nbreak and turning, but it&#39;s a", 
            "dur": "4.19", 
            "start": "426.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "really refined tool.", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "430.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A lot of engineers, prior to my\ntime, and during my time,", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "433.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and also, what I have done with\nthe car and all the other", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "436.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "people, there&#39;s a lot of effort\nput into it, that it", 
            "dur": "3.28", 
            "start": "439.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "should be very perfect\nin its behavior.", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "442.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we actually enjoy it when\npeople use their cars, because", 
            "dur": "4.29", 
            "start": "445.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that&#39;s what they are meant\nto do, to use them.", 
            "dur": "3.04", 
            "start": "449.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah we don&#39;t usually do\ndrifting or sliding for the", 
            "dur": "3.76", 
            "start": "457.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "purpose of sliding, but that\ncould be a byproduct of", 
            "dur": "3.1", 
            "start": "461.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "testing something\nelse, of course.", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "464.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when we do a lot of testing\non the limit for the", 
            "dur": "3.82", 
            "start": "466.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car to, for instance, prevent a\nbehavior of the car breaking", 
            "dur": "4.64", 
            "start": "470.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "out or spinning away too easy.", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "474.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then we need to go past that\npoint to really tell what", 
            "dur": "3.6", 
            "start": "477.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would happen and how\nthe car behaves.", 
            "dur": "1.535", 
            "start": "480.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we do all the adjusting\nand behavior.", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "492.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And how we would like\nthe car to feel is", 
            "dur": "3.7", 
            "start": "495.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "done without anything.", 
            "dur": "1.49", 
            "start": "498.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then we put ABS on, we put\ndouble train differential on,", 
            "dur": "3.62", 
            "start": "500.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we put the stability\ncontrol on.", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "503.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we only have those as you\nknow as your safety line,", 
            "dur": "4.27", 
            "start": "506.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "whatever you&#39;d like to call it,\nto prevent nasty things", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "510.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "from happening.", 
            "dur": "1.13", 
            "start": "513.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But if you would take everything\naway, we believe", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "514.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that the car as it is would\nbe very enjoyable for an", 
            "dur": "3.88", 
            "start": "517.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "experienced driver.", 
            "dur": "1.57", 
            "start": "521.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, you can be a good racing\ndriver and not be a good test", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "522.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "driver, and also the\nother way around.", 
            "dur": "2.63", 
            "start": "525.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because the race driver is not\nalways about feeling the car", 
            "dur": "4.75", 
            "start": "528.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "100% or putting very\ngood lap times.", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "533.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A race driver can be at the top,\nbecause he knows how to", 
            "dur": "3.17", 
            "start": "536.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fight his way through the field\nand he has a fast, a", 
            "dur": "4.08", 
            "start": "539.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "good pace enough to keep\nthat first place.", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "543.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that doesn&#39;t actually mean\nthat he needs to be the", 
            "dur": "2.8", 
            "start": "546.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fastest if he would go\nto a time attack.", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "549.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that&#39;s also the difference,\nthat you must want to learn", 
            "dur": "4.36", 
            "start": "551.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what is happening.", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "556.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And, of course, an input that\nsomething is understeer or", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "557.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "oversteer might be good enough\nfor an engineer.", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "559.786"
        }, 
        {
